<h2>Modules</h2>

<p>WebBlocks elements are organized into modules.</p>

<h3>Specifying Modules for Build</h3>

<p>By default, all modules in the <code>Base</code> and <code>Entity</code> namespaces are included in the WebBlocks build. However, one may specify only particular namespaces to include through the <code>WebBlocks.config[:src][:modules]</code> directive in <code>Rakefile-config.rb</code>.</p>

<p>As an example, this will include all <code>Base</code> modules and the <code>Entity/Form</code> module:</p>

<pre class="prettyprint">WebBlocks.config[:src][:modules] = []
WebBlocks.config[:src][:modules] << 'base'
WebBlocks.config[:src][:modules] << 'entity/form'</pre>

